name: SEARCH OF CONTENT
description:
“Search of content, no need for belief or disbelief, creation or disruption at its key. The search of something new. Frissons. Noyade.”

The search of something new, the search of something better, greater than you would expect. Looking outside the whole spectrum and reaching for something you are not in possession of currently. It is about imagination and desire. The sad truth of the past makes you aim in a completely whole new direction towards the future. Wether it is ordinary or unordinary you’ll always be searching for the content that animates your life. They progress as you get forward, create a dirt path to your destiny.
